### 1. 获取所有节点信息
GET http://localhost:5000/api/all_nodes

### 2. 获取当前掌握度
GET http://localhost:5000/api/get_status

### 3. 更新变量掌握度 85%
POST http://localhost:5000/api/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "node_name": "变量",
    "mastery": 0.85
}

### 4. 更新循环掌握度 45%
POST http://localhost:5000/api/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "node_name": "循环",
    "mastery": 0.45
}

### 5. 更新函数掌握度 20%
POST http://localhost:5000/api/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "node_name": "函数",
    "mastery": 0.20
}

### 6. 重置变量掌握度 0
POST http://localhost:5000/api/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "node_name": "变量",
    "mastery": 0
}